➜“搞定”英文怎么说？“搞”英文怎么翻译呢？
http://www.sohu.com/a/411274337_115013	1800
<p>不管什么语言</p>
<p>口语表达都会逐渐进化得非常简单</p>
<p>比如</p>
<p>把事情办理妥当了</p>
<p>口语就2个词</p>
<p>“搞定”</p>
<p>那，英文口语该怎么表达呢?</p>
<p>搞定nailed it</p>
<p>To succeed at something in a particularly impressive way.</p>
<p>以一种特别令人印象深刻的方式取得成功。</p>
<p>例：</p>
<p>A: "How was your interview today?"</p>
<p>你今天的面试怎么样?</p>
<p>B: "Nailed it."</p>
<p>完美搞定</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200803/b6691e3332104ee8a4ce60e9bcfbebd0.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>nail /neɪl/</p>
<p>nail本身作动词的意思是</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
